Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completly new features.

2005-07-26 bergie
    + Switched output to the xfolk microformat. See
      http://www.microformats.org/wiki/xfolk

2005-05-09 bergie
	+ Made all bookmarks hidden leaves to support searching

2005-05-03 bergie
    ! Switched bookmarklet URL from /topic/submitnewbookmark to /topic/submitbookmark
    + Added cache invalidation and indexing support to the bookmarklet
    + Added support for editing exiting bookmarks using the bookmarklet
    - Switched bookmark submission form to use datamanager styles

2005-04-16
	- Made translations and fixed some small problems
	- Added cache invalidation to viewer.php and admin.php
